# AUDIO::ENABLE_VEHICLE_FANBELT_DAMAGE

## Summary
Enable fanbelt damage (if the engine damage level gets high enough)

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
* **BOOL** enableFanbeltDamage
